										<span className="text-muted-foreground font-normal ml-1">
											(reps at cap)
										</span>
									)}
								</p>
								<div className="flex items-center gap-3 text-sm font-mono">
									<div className="text-center">
										<p className="text-muted-foreground text-[10px] uppercase">
											Original
